# portscan

A fast multithreaded port scanner with service banner grabbing. Pure Python, zero dependencies.

## Features

- TCP connect scan with multithreading
- Service banner grabbing on open ports
- Common port presets (top services)
- Full port range scan (1-65535)
- Custom port ranges
- JSON output
- Configurable thread count and timeout
- Real-time progress reporting

## Usage

### Scan common ports
```bash
python portscan.py 192.168.1.1
